==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Suburban
<hw>Sub*ur"ban</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>suburbanus</ets>.]</ety> <def>Of or pertaining to suburbs;
inhabiting, or being in, the suburbs of a city.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Suburban</xex> taverns.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Longfellow.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Suburban</qex> villas, highway-side retreats, . . . ⟦br⟧
Delight the citizen.</q> <rj><qau>Cowper.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Suburban</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Suburban
<hw>Sub*ur"ban</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who dwells in the
